{"tid":717250,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[求教][情景題] 比後車隊尾，但後車係因為第三架車撞埋去先隊到我，我應該claim邊個？","createTime":"2018-06-26T01:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T04:21:39.000Z","uid":78350,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d2cdf54d92c26b3b817a1fc0dbad59f1752d9a49","tid":717250,"uid":78350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早幾日渣車行50km 左右，前面架Benz 突然急停，本能反應加上high 到前面架Benz會好大獲嘅危機意識下，我曲速踩落個Brake度，最後幸好喺距離Benz 約 2 cm 嘅距離停低咗架車。<br />\n<br />\n可是，還未及時一抹額上冷汗之際，後方已傳來「呯」的一聲巨響，而司機位內的我亦感受到一記震蕩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同時意識到被後邊架車隊尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我氣沖沖咁落車諗住同個司機理論啦，一落車就見到後邊個司機面色唔係好咁，原來後車同時被後方一架紅Van 隊尾，佢架車後方個擋風玻璃爆晒，，車尾凹晒，應該醫返都晒藥費。<br />\n<br />\n了解之下原來佢本身係來得及停車，只係比紅Van 猛烈撞擊下先撞到我。<br />\n<br />\n差佬到場初步了解後話唔會告我，但就可能會告晒後邊兩架車。但如果查到係紅Van 司機撞到後車，然後先導致撞到我嘅話，就只會告紅Van司機。<br />\n<br />\n同後邊車司機交換電話號碼後我就走先，之後再傾賠償&hellip;因為當時個司機好唔舒服，我都唔好意思追問住。<br />\n<br />\n返到去check 返自己架車，後門凹咗，sensor壞咗 (明明關晒門，錶板仲顯示住未關上門嘅icon)，Bumper 鬆脫，唔算太嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n好喇，故事講完，多謝大家留心。問題係：我而家應該點做？<br />\n<br />\n應該同咗後車司機傾賠償先？還是同個紅Van司機傾？<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過又有人教唔好整架車住，搵公正行評估損失先&hellip;但公正行條數係邊個孭？<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打試過類似情況，求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4896c024cadda86fae2ef1815ce0eefefb1bd7","tid":717250,"uid":21664,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"好似係現場影相做證據幾重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我9up"},{"pid":"b1cf57e879cc0d12d7affc865df46ebf00a93408","tid":717250,"uid":56159,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"試過9車連環撞 最尾個架賠晒"},{"pid":"2559e1b2263b8bc1bd53729651ef82083d7d7ec6","tid":717250,"uid":9838,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:41:36.000Z","msg":"無記錯 你照claim後車，而後車會claim返尾車"},{"pid":"86b4a15b7d4e45e640f713932de76fcfa46ae7b6","tid":717250,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:43:29.000Z","msg":"學術答案: 後車 (因為係佢撞你)<br />\n現實答案: 第三車 (因為後車會告佢，你要等後車索償到先有錢分)"},{"pid":"f91aa7abc58a1813aac368fbc00cf086a3705b1b","tid":717250,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:43:43.000Z","msg":"btw 傾乜撚賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一時間報保險，佢會教你點做"},{"pid":"d13bb8bdcefd233fc478f7f6942886191b3bf759","tid":717250,"uid":141367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1cf57e879cc0d12d7affc865df46ebf00a93408","tid":717250,"uid":56159,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"試過9車連環撞 最尾個架賠晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:43:54.000Z","msg":"早幾個月果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"887819a30b1cad86716828be3fbbde15bbbd4cd0","tid":717250,"uid":112583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2559e1b2263b8bc1bd53729651ef82083d7d7ec6","tid":717250,"uid":9838,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:41:36.000Z","msg":"無記錯 你照claim後車，而後車會claim返尾車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:45:29.000Z","msg":"正解, 邊個撞你claim邊個<br />\n你冇權力去判尾車有冇犯錯<br />\n所以你只可以claim撞你個架"},{"pid":"0396d9908e277d9957cbf03415e51fceaeb1a76d","tid":717250,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:46:49.000Z","msg":"希望樓主有報保險啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1abbca5499ef7cfdca325ff120d0029cd9faeba","tid":717250,"uid":25118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:49:02.000Z","msg":"你只需要 claim 後車，佢會 claim 尾車兩條數，1. 尾車撞到佢嘅直接損失，2. 尾車令後車撞到你架車引起嘅賠償<br />\n架車唔好自己整，check 下差佬有無即場收走你車 cam 片，報保險公司，佢會教你點做"},{"pid":"de66e763c6ad938ab1201b694a6af64db463e4b9","tid":717250,"uid":25118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"記住唔好搞架車維持原狀，公證行都唔好自己搵住，問咗保險公司先，有朋友試過自己搵公證行但保險公司話唔係佢地指定嘅唔認數，要再搵返佢指定果間做多次..."},{"pid":"e0ba6b7f343b0a7bcc222fbc568f78bceffe321e","tid":717250,"uid":78350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0396d9908e277d9957cbf03415e51fceaeb1a76d","tid":717250,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:46:49.000Z","msg":"希望樓主有報保險啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:18:29.000Z","msg":"我只買咗第三保&hellip;報就報咗，但無乜用&hellip;"},{"pid":"5a70e16c71bccf220f37c4e28f669ed28ed4c589","tid":717250,"uid":78350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1abbca5499ef7cfdca325ff120d0029cd9faeba","tid":717250,"uid":25118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:49:02.000Z","msg":"你只需要 claim 後車，佢會 claim 尾車兩條數，1. 尾車撞到佢嘅直接損失，2. 尾車令後車撞到你架車引起嘅賠償<br />\n架車唔好自己整，check 下差佬有無即場收走你車 cam 片，報保險公司，佢會教你點做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"唔該晒師兄&hellip;我報咗保險喇<br />\n<br />\n架車唔好自己整嘅意思係等後車司機幫我整？還是搵咗公正行驗傷先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f651d1f8104626a92d422081c4452985a3f1b3d","tid":717250,"uid":78350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"887819a30b1cad86716828be3fbbde15bbbd4cd0","tid":717250,"uid":112583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2559e1b2263b8bc1bd53729651ef82083d7d7ec6","tid":717250,"uid":9838,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:41:36.000Z","msg":"無記錯 你照claim後車，而後車會claim返尾車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2